WEBVTT

00:01.560 --> 00:04.119
Two traffic officers
were first at the scene.

00:04.120 --> 00:05.729
<i>They found three bodies -</i>

00:05.730 --> 00:07.699
two young women
and an elderly man.

00:07.700 --> 00:10.949
<i>Another body's since been
found in a burnt out four-by-four.</i>

00:10.950 --> 00:13.450
- Hello, Bluebell.
- Get away from her!

00:14.760 --> 00:16.309
My father...

00:16.309 --> 00:18.279
He's the one to blame.

00:18.280 --> 00:20.499
<i>- Mel has gone to the hospital.</i>
- Is she OK?

00:20.500 --> 00:23.009
- She's been shot.
- Has she said anything?

00:23.010 --> 00:25.449
It was Andy.
<i>He's on the run.</i>

00:25.450 --> 00:27.579
One of the lorries is
unaccounted for.

00:27.580 --> 00:29.399
Right, and I bet I know who's got that.

00:29.400 --> 00:31.259
Apart from finding out
where Andy is,

00:31.260 --> 00:34.459
<i>identifying who
he was with is our main priority.</i>

00:34.460 --> 00:36.779
- Any idea who this is?
- Yeah, we've got him.

00:36.780 --> 00:38.209
Michael Adams.

00:38.210 --> 00:40.899
Listen, I can only give you
24 hours on this, OK?

00:40.900 --> 00:43.299
<i>The gun you found under the dead
man's car seat,</i>

00:43.300 --> 00:45.399
- it's not been sent over.
- It's evidence.

00:45.400 --> 00:48.189
<i>Evidence that the gun
is police issue.</i>

00:48.190 --> 00:50.389
<i>This is all wrong,</i>
Clarissa.

00:50.390 --> 00:52.500
All wrong.

00:54.000 --> 01:00.074
